name: "Nobody Creeper (Animated)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Liner pen on notebook page with digital embellishments, color, and moshing.] The horror is that it recognized that it should HAVE a body, but it wasn't familiar enough WITH bodies to know what it actually meant to inhabit one. It tried to fabricate a form, so that it could interact with the simple creatures of the strange new dimension that it had discovered, but it failed... Failed spectacularly... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
